<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">عِكْرِمَةَ قَالَ:</span> أَوَّلُ الْفَتْحِ: يَوْمَ الشَّجَرَةِ،<span class="c5"> وَالآخِرُ:</span> يَوْمَ فَتْحِ مَكَّةَ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>